/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Monty Rakusen</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The mining sector is looking toward a year where the threat of tariffs may be balanced by potential stimulus, declining costs and a growing interest in uranium. MoneyTalk\u2019s Anthony Okolie discusses with Craig Hutchison, Director, Equity Research, TD Cowen.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/150639576/image_150639576.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743765-tariffs-stimulus-other-potential-catalysts-for-mining-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 13:30:00"}, {"id": "4743811", "title": "Allspring Core Plus Bond Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1952157073/image_1952157073.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Futuristic digital background. Hexagon shell with binary code and glowing dollar sign. Protection 